videos.description: Ole Miss QB Matt Corral fumbles the ball on a handoff attempt on fourth down, and Arkansas jumps on the ball to keep the game scoreless.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss fumbles handoff as Arkansas gets goal-line stop) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss fumbles handoff as Arkansas gets goal-line stop

videos.description: Rakeem Boyd gets Arkansas' first rushing touchdown of the season to open the scoring against Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Boyd crams his way into the end zone for the 1-yard TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boyd crams his way into the end zone for the 1-yard TD

videos.description: Arkansas's Jalen Catalon perfectly jumps the route to intercept Matt Corral's pass and score a 35-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Catalon comes up with pick-six for Arkansas) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Catalon comes up with pick-six for Arkansas

videos.description: Elijah Moore has to stretch out to haul in the 7-yard reception, but he makes the catch and puts the Rebels on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moore's tumbling catch gets Ole Miss a TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moore's tumbling catch gets Ole Miss a TD

videos.description: Matt Corral connects with Jonathan Mingo for the easy touchdown reception inching Ole Miss closer to Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rebels score again with a 21-yard TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rebels score again with a 21-yard TD

videos.description: Treylon Burks reels in the one-handed, 7-yard touchdown catch at the back of the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burks stays in with outrageous one-handed toe-tapping TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burks stays in with outrageous, one-handed, toe-tapping TD

videos.description: Matt Corral's pass gets picked off again for another defensive touchdown to extend the Razorbacks' lead again.

videos.headline: Morgan comes up with a 23-yard pick-six for Arkansas

videos.description: In a turnover-heavy contest, the ascending Razorbacks create seven turnovers (6 INTs) to defeat Ole Miss 33-21.
videos.headline: Hogs pick off Corral six times in win over Rebels
